{"tid":337534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱一早見被告　警庭上改口","createTime":"2017-07-27T11:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T12:46:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"663ac4e778f46dcc517dce7ad838d8bbe6588ed7","tid":337534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20102689&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20102689%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170727&d=ALUAnwbwHc4NfDmR6FIHkdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=bdad4f2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20102689%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170727&h=f7e35d13\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20102689&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170727</a><br />\n<br />\n稱一早見被告　警庭上改口<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告關兆宏<br />\n<br />\n【刑事藐視法庭案】<br />\n【本報訊】社民連黃浩銘及8人涉嫌於大前年在旺角佔領區清場時未按禁制令離開，否認刑事藐視法庭罪，案件昨在高院續審。拘捕被告關兆宏的警員稱，到現場不久已留意關，當時約上午8時45分，後將關抬走拘捕。惟辯方指關9時45分才到場，而片段亦看到關被捕時被押走，而非抬走。警員聞言改口稱對看到關的時間「唔肯定」，亦同意沒將他抬起。<br />\n<br />\n指時間「係咁上下啦」<br />\n<br />\n警員梁偉雄的口供指，他遂與其他警員將被告關兆宏抬起拘捕。辯方盤問時播放警方片段，片中可見關與黃浩銘、黃之鋒等人站一起，有警司突撲出拘捕黃之鋒，警員一擁而上，此時關亦被捕。梁同意未開始拘捕前已留意到關，「佢一直企喺黃之鋒隔籬」，但表明當時「冇話邊個要拉邊個」。辯方又指梁聲稱見到關的時間，與關實際到場相差一小時，梁聞言僅稱時間「係咁上下啦」。辯方再指出警方較早時間片段中都看不到關的身影，梁才改口稱「咁我唔肯定」。<br />\n案件編號：HCMP778、780、783、784、788、789、791、796、798/15<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣"},{"pid":"2c5f64e39aff9c299f41bd377efc69bf1cccb1a5","tid":337534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170727/large/27ls3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170727%2Flarge%2F27ls3p4.jpg&h=89df77e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告關兆宏"},{"pid":"472b98d855f364b8c0eb75c3e26de14ff7e5b4a6","tid":337534,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290039586720b237da1ce572168cdbf6373b0123","tid":337534,"uid":57636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:46:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}